00:43:43.749 --> 00:43:46.719
for my app and I promote that through YouTube.

00:43:46.719 --> 00:43:51.619
I might not necessarily get a ton of people
to buy it but I create a lot of awareness.

00:43:51.619 --> 00:43:52.619
Why?

00:43:52.619 --> 00:43:56.690
Because a picture is worth a thousand words
and a video is worth a thousand pictures.

00:43:56.690 --> 00:43:57.920
That's brand awareness.

00:43:57.920 --> 00:43:59.339
That's brand advertising.

00:43:59.339 --> 00:44:04.240
TV, outdoor, YouTube, videos, that's brand
awareness.

00:44:04.240 --> 00:44:05.319
How do you measure that stuff?

00:44:05.319 --> 00:44:07.869
You might ask, why on earth would I do this?

00:44:07.869 --> 00:44:09.470
I need to be able to measure this.

00:44:09.470 --> 00:44:12.660
If I do an AdMob campaign, I can measure the
clicks.

00:44:12.660 --> 00:44:14.839
That's true, but you can measure brand.

00:44:14.839 --> 00:44:16.880
It's a different way of doing it.

00:44:16.880 --> 00:44:20.700
Essentially what you need to do is you run
what's called a brand tracker which can be

00:44:20.700 --> 00:44:25.459
very simple exercise of asking three to four
questions to your base of consumers every

00:44:25.459 --> 00:44:27.079
single month.

00:44:27.079 --> 00:44:31.019
And you ask them questions like, for example,
among the following kinds of sports apps,

00:44:31.019 --> 00:44:32.700
which have you heard of?

00:44:32.700 --> 00:44:35.519
You list all the apps, yours and your competitors.

00:44:35.519 --> 00:44:37.759
That's aided brand awareness.

00:44:37.759 --> 00:44:41.950
You can ask another question which is, which
sports apps have you heard of in general?

00:44:41.950 --> 00:44:43.890
That's unaided brand awareness.

00:44:43.890 --> 00:44:48.170
You can ask questions, for example, of in
the next four weeks, do you intend to purchase

00:44:48.170 --> 00:44:49.869
a sports app?

00:44:49.869 --> 00:44:51.140
That's purchase intent.

00:44:51.140 --> 00:44:53.849
So there are a lot of ways to measure brand
awareness.

00:44:53.849 --> 00:44:57.489
