00:45:06.059 --> 00:45:13.380
So tip number four: Search at least for us
when we are promoting the Google Play store

00:45:13.380 --> 00:45:18.680
has been one of the most effective ways to
actually advertise.

00:45:18.680 --> 00:45:20.500
Why?

00:45:20.500 --> 00:45:24.170
First of all, because the click through rate,
which our colleagues previously mentioned,

00:45:24.170 --> 00:45:27.349
is higher on search generally than any other
medium.

00:45:27.349 --> 00:45:28.519
Why is that?

00:45:28.519 --> 00:45:31.489
Because search is an active advertising form.

00:45:31.489 --> 00:45:35.430
Search basically provides a request, provides
information to a consumer who is already looking

00:45:35.430 --> 00:45:38.140
for something specific.

00:45:38.140 --> 00:45:43.609
Therefore, the odds are that that person is
more interested in that result because it's

00:45:43.609 --> 00:45:46.259
specific to what they are looking for.

00:45:46.259 --> 00:45:50.160
If I do a search on sports apps and I see
your app and I'm interested in sports, the

00:45:50.160 --> 00:45:52.059
probability is higher that I'm going to download
that.

00:45:52.059 --> 00:45:56.640
That's going to be more cost effective for
you and higher probability that that person

00:45:56.640 --> 00:45:59.569
is actually going to install your application.

00:45:59.569 --> 00:46:03.880
Typically, what would you expect from a good
