00:46:30.990 --> 00:46:32.319
it's a passive experience.

00:46:32.319 --> 00:46:34.309
I'm either interested in or I'm not.

00:46:34.309 --> 00:46:37.759
But I'm not specifically making a proactive
search for it, so I'm probably not looking

00:46:37.759 --> 00:46:39.079
for your application.

00:46:39.079 --> 00:46:45.829
Web site typically a good response rate for
Mobile ad campaign can be .5, .6, .7, .8%

00:46:45.829 --> 00:46:50.099
CTR, vastly different from what you would
